target.message: Version 1.1.0. mgf module added. Also, minor fixes in docs.
Add pandas to optdepends in pkgbuild

Fix namespace-related issues in pepxml.
The solution is a bit hacky, but it's the best I could think of by now.
We use local-name() in XPath queries everywhere to avoid node names
altogether.
Add decoy_prefix and decoy_suffix to protxml tests. Version 3.5
Fix again the issue with mzML from CompassXport
Add iterfind instead of _itertag in XML-reading modules
Fix pepxml test to work with new API. Fix float_keys bug in new API
New example; rename parser.peptide_length to length
Bump version to update doc link on PyPI
Rename parse_sequence to parse, incorporate Anton's changes. 2.0beta
